163
00:09:34,470 --> 00:09:35,460
克莱尔
Claire.

164
00:09:38,310 --> 00:09:40,920
抱歉  我没写信向你表示悼念...
I'm sorry I didn't write after Francis--

165
00:09:40,920 --> 00:09:42,990
